step.template-output:
Generate epics and stories document. Each story formatted as:
### Story {epic-N}-{story-N}: {Title}
- Epic: {epic name}
- Priority: {P0/P1/P2}
- Size: {S/M/L/XL}
- Risk: {high/medium/low}
- Depends on: [{story-ids}]
- Blocks: [{story-ids}]
- Acceptance Criteria:
  - AC1: {criteria}
